{
  "stem": "27150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we took a cab to the airport to-- I'm sorry, to the, to the railway station and came over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By that time, it was four or five o'clock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He already came with his wagon, horse wagon, with the things and were settling our sales.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the kids were collecting kindling and pines, chasing squirrels.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a big sort of entertainment, going out to the railway track and counting the track, the cars, and the freight were railways.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you see, this, they used to do it year after year after year.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the one I remember was in, must have been in 1920, you know, because you see, we were watching the telegraph wires and were waiting until a telegram comes through, which never comes, only sort of birds perching.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And news came that Trotzky is coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Oh, I didn't know who Trotsky was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But you see, some people say he is a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we thought that it was sort of kind of a devil.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And you see, that means we gave the farmer, you know, to put on the stuff on the wagon.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we came, we went to Warsaw by the narrow gauge railway, because the wide railway was carrying troops, et cetera, et cetera, which I found out later.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At that time, I wouldn't know why.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I just take it for granted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We came to east Warsaw, which was called Praga.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And across the bridge, you see, carrying that little parcels.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And well, the five-- that means the three of us and mother, because the kid, all the kids were already in Warsaw, for they went a few days later.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we took a horse cab who came to the courtyard, you see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And nothing was sort of changed.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
